  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Located on Levi fell, approx. 4km by road from Levi resort centre. The convenient Levi Summit gondola takes guests directly from Hotel Levi Panorama to Levi centre in less than 5 minutes. Guests receive a free day ticket for each day of their stay (excluding day of arrival or departure). The gondola runs from 9:30am - 11pm daily.</p>
<p>The Hotel Panorama Apartments are located next to the main hotel building.</p>]]></locationDescription>
