  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are around 28m² can sleep two to four people (recommended for three adults or two adults and two children) in twin beds, with a divan sofa bed which can be converted to two extra single beds for full occupancy. This room can be located on any floor and has a ski slope view. Standard rooms are also available for single occupancy at a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are around 33m² and can sleep two to four people (recommended for three adults or two adults and two children) in twin beds with a balcony and drying closet. There is a divan sofa bed which can sleep either one adult or two children. Superior rooms can be located on any floor, facing the front hotel courtyard. Also available for single occupancy at a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Suite</strong> are around 52m² and can sleep two to four people. These Suites have a twin bedroom and a living area with a double sofa bed which can sleep one adult or two children, and a French balcony (excluding some rooms on the 2nd floor) facing the courtyard and Kätkä fell.</p>
<p>All of the hotel rooms are located in the main building and are furnished in a modern style.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Panorama Apartments</strong></p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments</strong> are around 45-50m² and can sleep two to five people. These apartments have one twin bedroom plus an alcove with bunk beds (120cm double bed on lower bunk and single bed on upper bunk - suitable for two adults or up to three children under 12yrs)</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Apartments</strong> are around 65m² sleeping three to six people. These apartments have two twin bedrooms plus a double sofa bed in the living room (suitable for one adult or two children).</p>
<p>The apartments are located next to the main hotel building.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Private sauna</li>
<li>Fully-equipped kitchen with fridge, oven, microwave, kettle, coffee maker, dishwasher and toaster plus washing machine</li>
<li>TV with DVD player</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Drying Closet</li>
<li>Private shower and WC</li>
<li>Linen and towels</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
